ngue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eb804edd38806354778570fab8a106580ce646","tid":380453,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行神室町仲熟過銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莎木1橫須賀 莎木2香港 莎木3桂林<br />\n會轉場景已經夠正，藍帝東亞復仇團"},{"pid":"cb68389af689830a5ba8ee561c46bd30b681cf7b","tid":380453,"uid":8858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>莎木剩係每個npc都有自己既生活已經完爆人中<br />\n人中d街角真係鳩行完就算</blockquote><br />\nnpc仲大量對白，1999年已經全配音<br />\n有開閂舖時間，過咗明天請早"},{"pid":"eb5d282fca14f00a47ac054073154f00059ba6ff","tid":380453,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人中係莎木低成本試作點知又受歡迎<br />\n咁大家自然對莎木期待</blockquote><br />\n莎木一已經有全語音360度第一身視角 <br />\n商品可以直接拎上手睇<br />\n機舖打機會有埋動畫見主角埋去打機，唔係眼前一黑就開始<br />\n日夜隨時間轉換唔同景色，天氣會隨遊戲日子跟當年地方天氣報告轉變天氣會落雨 落雪<br />\n仲有聖誕節聖誕老人到新年npc會換和服出街<br />\nNpc全人物都可以交談，全語音，唔同日子或者觸發唔同劇情都有唔同對白<br />\n細節多成本自然貴好多，咁多野俾其他廠抽晒嚟用已經變到好平常"},{"pid":"b93931ca9cf90140d6ad9b35e32f8a2e10d85b26","tid":380453,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"係&quot;玩&quot;既角度人中好過莎木（特別係1）真係多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fc95ec72c139edeab8013d87fe314a9f400e8e","tid":380453,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係&quot;玩&quot;既角度人中好過莎木（特別係1）真係多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莎木1節奏太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係點對點或者提晒水做咩，要自己搵相關人物問寫筆記先知道點樣推進到故事玩法太創新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莎木1打鬥又唔多冇人週街挑你機練功就自high，到莎2就cut埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莎木1時間未到或者過咗就要搵地方hea太現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到2已經改善可以加快時間直接夠鐘<br />\n對遊戲講唔多似玩係要生活喺裡面，所以1同2各有愛好者，唔知3又點改法"},{"pid":"311072c2d7d276a306c613e09e86c7fccd379aa4","tid":380453,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"驚整唔返莎木1 2 既感覺"},{"pid":"9d73aea0623bb611468ce01b87916cc2b6c0d20f","tid":380453,"uid":16870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93931ca9cf90140d6ad9b35e32f8a2e10d85b26","tid":380453,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"係&quot;玩&quot;既角度人中好過莎木（特別係1）真係多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"如果淨係想打交當然悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開段當自己偵探咁搵仇人線索我覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}